      "Architected and implemented OAuth 2.0 and OpenID Connect authentication system, enabling SSO across multiple enterprise applications",
      "Led development of the Task Manager module, coordinating a team of 4 developers using agile methodologies",
      "Designed and built comprehensive reporting modules for Strategy, Acquisition, Business and Claim Management",
      "Successfully coordinated database migration from Oracle to PostgreSQL, reducing licensing costs by 60%",
      "Migrated application server from Glassfish to Payara, improving performance and maintainability",
      "Established CI/CD pipelines with GitLab, reducing deployment time from days to hours",
      "Mentored junior developers and conducted code reviews to maintain code quality",
