      "Developed 2 enterprise applications for internal deployment with offline-first capabilities",
      "Built 2 social media applications with real-time messaging and media sharing",
      "Created a dating application with location-based matching and chat features",
      "Worked directly with clients to gather requirements and deliver solutions",
    ],
  },
  {
    company: "RF Silicon Pvt Ltd",
    role: "Software Development Intern",
    period: "Dec. 2013 - May 2014",
    location: "New Delhi/Noida, India",
    description: "Specialized in Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) development for IoT healthcare devices.",
