          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            I specialize in <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">full-stack development</strong> with Java and React, with deep expertise in enterprise architecture, security (OAuth/OIDC), and DevOps practices. I'm passionate about writing clean, maintainable code and building systems that scale.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            When I'm not coding, you'll find me cycling through the Bavarian countryside, playing badminton, or exploring new technologies. I believe in continuous learning and sharing knowledge with the community.
          </p>

          <!-- Quick Stats -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-8">
            <div class="text-center p-4 rounded-xl bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold gradient-text">7+</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Years Experience</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-4 rounded-xl bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold gradient-text">15+</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Projects Delivered</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-4 rounded-xl bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold gradient-text">3</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Countries Worked</div>
