            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Frontend Development</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">Creating responsive, accessible user interfaces with React, TypeScript, and modern CSS. User experience first.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card p-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-950 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
              </svg>
