            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Security & Auth</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">Implementing OAuth 2.0, OpenID Connect, and enterprise security patterns. Protecting applications and data.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card p-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-950 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Database Design</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">Designing efficient database schemas, migrations, and optimizations. PostgreSQL specialist with Oracle experience.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card p-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-950 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
