              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">DevOps & CI/CD</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">Setting up automated pipelines with GitLab CI/CD, Docker, and cloud deployments. Streamlining development workflows.</p>
          </div>

